  <brief_title>Risk Factors for Predictors of In-hospital Death in Acute Fulminant Myocarditis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Risk Factors Influenced Prognosis of Acute Fulminant Myocarditis by Analyzing Clinical Characteristics and Complications, Laboratory Findings, Treatments, and Electrocardiographic and Echocardiographic Data.</official_title>
